V,δp is the pth percentile of hourly data of variable V for the decade δ. Here, a decade is a meteorological expression and is defined as a sequence of 8, 9, 10, or 11 days (a month is subdivided into three decades with decade 1 including days 1–10, decade 2 days 11–20, and decade 3 the rest).

